review_title: Just as good as other brands
reviews: I have a few of these now from different brands, and this one is just as good, not much complication in a plastic jug that holds water, it does its job and holds water, what more can you ask for?
3rd time I have bought this brand for 3 different phones, good quality at a good price, can't beat that!

I really liked this heater at first but 2 months in use now and it doesn't work correctly anymore, save your money and buy a different one. I would return it if I could.

Problems with this heater:

- It is not accurate, or consistent, may as not even have a temperature knob as it doesn't work.
- 2 months of use and water is leaking into the inside glass which makes this heater no long useful in anyway

This is the first time I have used this brand of heater and will be the last. I decided to give it a try as I have liked other Hydor products in the past but this heater is no good, I would not recommend it to anyone.
Perfect way to test for chlorine to see when its time to replace carbon block in my ro system for my aquarium. Quick and easy to read strips.
One sachet is perfect in a glass of water, easy to take on the go, adds just enough flavor to water, no too much not too little, its perfect solution to adding a bit of lemon taste to your water.

My bearded dragon loves these, its by far his favorite food item. If you have a younger bearded dragon or smaller lizard these might be too big, they are on the large side so suitable for adult bearded dragons and larger lizards but not so much for smaller lizards or young bearded dragons.

review_title: Works for both chelated and non-chelated iron
reviews:
Unlike some test kits for iron this one works with both chelated and non-chelated iron which makes it more useful. It's easy to use and only takes 1 minute to get results for non-chelated iron, but does take 30 minutes to get the result for chelated iron, so depending on what iron supplement your using you need to make sure you know if it contained chelated or non-chelated iron so you know how long to wait for the final result. Also there is a little plastic spoon included that is easily lost when opening the package so keep an eye out for it as you need it for the powder reagent.

Overall its an excellent test and great value and accurate, makes dosing iron in a planted tank much easier.

review_title: Not impressed after 3 months of use
reviews:
I have been using this light for 3 months and not impressed with it. I ended up getting a known brand in the end.

The price for this light is okay, but if looking for long term and quality, better to just buy a known brand first time around.

The light gets extremely hot as does the power box, the remote is a pain to use as you have to be close to the power box and its still finicky, and because the sensor is in the power box, need to always have it accessible and can't hide it since the only way the remote will work is if your literally pointing it at the power box.

The color isn't as good at a known brand, and the shimmer effect while not bad, isn't good either.

Overall if you want a light for a nano reef, I would go with Kessil or another known brand, in the end you will save money.

If the return window was still open, I would return this light.

These work great in air driven protein skimmers. I have a reef glass skimmer and some of the other brands don't fit and its hard to get the reef glass air stones, but these fit, and leave enough room for expansion to not damage the skimmer, and they work just as good if not better than the reef glass air stone. No complaints and good value for 2.
Dog loves them, only one ingredient and no fillers.

I have replaced all my air pumps with various sizes of Tetra pumps and have found these pumps to work well, are quieter than many other brands and strong. I've never had any issues with this brand of air pump over the years, and they are a great price typically which is even better.

I really like these, they work well, don't lose connection, battery lasts me the day, comfortable to wear and good noise cancelling with excellent sound quality. No complaints about these at all, they are excellent quality at a good price.

I have had this for a couple months now, and it simply doesn't work correctly, guess the old saying you get what you pay for it correct. I would spend the extra on a better quality known brand, you will save money in the long run.
It was easy to read and was accurate but the one I received only last about 2 months, wouldn't recommend.

review_title: Not a powder, doesn't stick to insects well.
reviews: This product smells like rabbit food, but anyhow I am sure its a good product, but its not very fine and doesn't stick to insects well, does okay when sprinkled over my dragons salad but pretty useless for insects so I ended up buying another brand, if you need it to dust insects this may not be the best choice.

I prefer media bags with a zipper over the usual ones, this is a perfect media bags, hold a lot of media of your choice, and the zipper securely closes it, the zipper is plastic so no worries about metal or rust. Perfect solution if you prefer buying media in bulk over pre-packaged.

I was looking for a secondary heat source for my bearded dragon as I found the usual heat lamps didn't quite get his hot side warm enough, this little light was the perfect solution, takes up little space, includes spring hooks to secure it to the top of an enclosure, seems like its well built.

Only been using it a few days, but it gets hot, and test will be to see how long the bulb lasts. Also keep in mine the bulbs are sold separately as they have different options, I got the daylight white bulb.

I'll update when the bulb burns out or in 6 months whichever occurs first.
Perfect cut to fit sponge for my filter, comes with both fine and course sponges and works perfect for my need.

I needed a T5 fixture for my reptile UVB but didn't want to spend the 70+ reptile marketed one's sell for, this one actually works better, nice and sleek and good quality. I am very happy with this product.

Perfect little desk top heater, have been using it for a couple weeks now and produces a nice amount of heat, it is small and compact and perfect if looking for a heater that will sit on a desk or other small area.

review_title: Produces a good amount of air, pretty quiet.
reviews: I am happy with the amount of air this pump produces, and overall it's pretty quiet, it sits in my stand under the tank and I can't hear the pump itself, happy with this pump.

review_title: Very little dust, easy to rinse and use
reviews: Very little dust which makes rinsing super easy and simple, well made, and porous and perfect fit for what I needed, better than other brands on the market.

Despite saying its standard size on the packaging its not, I tried to use it with 2 different name brand air pumps and it doesn't fit either, and the check valves I have also do not fit this tubing, its smaller diameter than standard size so buy with caution as it may not fit your air pump/airstone/devices.
For the price I got these for, they are worth it, nice color, keeps enough light out so I can sleep and looks good, they do come a little wrinkled but no biggie.
My fish love this food, good wholesome ingredients and not filled with fillers like cheaper foods are, highly recommend.

This is an easy to use timer, easy to set. Impressed so far with this timer and might be a couple more as its much easier to set compared to some of the other digital timers I have used.

Update: April 11, 2020

So after 5 months of use, the timer stopped working. It was certainly easy to set and worked well for 5 months but just stopped working today, still shows the time, but no longer turns lights on and off, so seems this timer could be short lived, maybe I got a dud, I don't know, but a timer should last longer than 5 months. It was used indoors so not exposed to any weather or extreme temps or anything.

I needed a couple of these for my aquarium and was having trouble finding some that would work, these work for my needs and overall so far happy with them, they seem well made, they arrived well packaged in a box, and good value in my view.

The clip that holds it to the aquarium is on the larger side but its not of concern to me, does the job its supposed and works with a framed aquarium where other brands only work on rimless so that is a plus.

I will update in 6 months of use.

review_title: Easy to set up and use.
reviews: I have not been using this item long term so cant speak to long term use, but so far I am happy with it. It was easy to set up, and has been working well so far. I will update in a few months if any issues arise.
These work really well. I love them, perfect for the bathroom to hold small items, perfect solution, easy to use and strong suction power.
Good size and quality. Was perfect for my needs in setting up a riparium.

I had been using sea chem line but wasn't getting the results I wanted, been using this product now since July 2019 and quite impressed with it, will be buying again. One of the best fertilizers you can buy.

Its a good filter, I have used this brand and style of filter before with good results. I bought the 40i model and it was perfect for my needs, only down side is they only include 1 suction cup but 2 is needed if you dont want to use the provided hook, otherwise I have no complaints, just know that you will need to call Tetra or have suction cups already when buying this item, if your going to use the hook no issue though.

Update: Only a few days of using and its now incredibly loud. I have used these filters before and never had one this noisy, so maybe its defective, I checked the pump and everything is secured, but it way too loud for my needs.

review_title: Good quality, but missing suction cup.
reviews: I gave 4 stars as the item itself is good quality and I like the product, but Amazon is sending them out with 1 suction cup missing, Amazon did send a replacement but it also only had 1 suction cup but as they didn't require the original to be sent back, it worked out in the end, but both I received had 1 suction cup missing, and it requires 2 to function correctly, so keep that in mind. Hopefully amazon will notice this and stop sending them out with missing suctions cups.
Seems well made, so far happy with it.
Works well, cleaned the dishwasher well and has a pleasent scent. Will use again.
Can't really go wrong with clay balls, these work and do what they are made for,

I have found this scale good so far, I tested it with a 10 pound weight and it was spot on so seems accurate, easy clear read out, good scale for the price, and takes a normal AA battery instead of the little button battery some brands use.

Edit Nov 25, 2019 After a few weeks the scale stopped being accurate, and calibrating it would not solve the problem, used a known 5 pound weight and got anywhere from 5 pounds to 8 pounds, when I weighed myself got anything from 190 to 240 when trying it several times in a row. Returned it to Amazon as there was no way to fix it, and well after only a couple weeks for it to already be acting up, not worth keeping.
I am happy with this heater, works and keeps the temp at an accurate temp, so far so good.
Good mouse, comfortable to use. Battery seems to have decent life.
Nice soap for the kitchen or bathroom, gentle on my skin and has a nice scent, quite happy with this soap and will buy again.
It's a nice well made sock, comfortable to wear.

This pump is quiet with good flow, perfect for my 4 gallon aquarium, I wouldn't use it on anything much larger than 5 gallons though, its got good flow and can be adjusted easily. Quiet, I can't hear it running.

I like this pump so much I bought another, its a great little pump.
My fish like this food, and eagerly eat it, good size for a betta. Only downside is it sinks really fast and the fish are not always able to get it because it sinks so fast.

I have only been using this light short term but will update in a few months, but so far its a nice little light. Fits a small tank perfectly, pretty bright for its size and a nice natural looking light. Pretty impressed for the price point.

I needed a heater for a small all in one aquarium with limited space, this was one of the only ones I could find. So far so good, this review is based on short term use, I will update later on once I have some long term use from it, but so far I am happy with this heater, its keeping the tank in the 77-78F range which is exactly the range I wanted, downside is there is no temp control and it's pre-set but all the small heaters seem to made that way.

It's not a bad siphon, good for very small tanks, but the suction is pretty weak so wouldn't use it for anything more then 1 or 2 gallons in size, I think even 5 gallons would be pushing it. Its well made and good quality, just too small for good suction.
Good price and a good bulb, gives a nice natural light.
I bought this item for work as I work outside, seems well made, fits well. No complaints.

I work on the ramp around aircraft and I always found this brand and type of ear plugs to be the most comfortable while also working well, great for noise reduction when working in a noisy environment, very comfortable to wear.
Seems like a good well built case, so far happy with it. Have to see how it works long term, but so far so good.

Not a bad cover for the price, its a flexible soft material, and likely wouldn't provide a ton of protection from a serious drop, but will provide protection from everyday normal use, not bad for the price.

We have a miniature dachshund and this ramp is perfect for her so she can get on/off a queen bed of normal height. Built well and is sturdy and perfect for small-medium sized dogs, the carpeting material is a soft plastic mesh type material and out dog has no issues with it, its nicely padded and provides enough grip so she can easily go up and down the ramp.

The ramp comes ready to use, no building necessary, just unfold, lock and ready to go. Literally took maybe 2 minutes to open, and set up. Very easy to use.
I really like Taylor Swift music and not disappointed.

This product does work but use some caution, don't just blinding follow the directions just use it as a guide. Luckily I was testing the product first before using it in my aquariums, but if I had followed the directions as they are on the label it would not have been good. It's a good product but best to smart small and see how much you actually need to use to get the parameters your looking to get.

I ended up only needing about 30% of the stated amount in the directions to get to where I needed.

It's not a great filter, but its an okay filter. Wish I had gone with a different one. It works, but the suction cups suck and the filter keeps falling off, and the plastic clips that hold the filter on instead of the suction cups broke within the first couple of days. If you can try a different filter.

I am not a professional and just needed a simple inexpensive tripod and this ones hit all the marks, its sturdier and better built then I was expecting. Excellent value for the price. May not work for the pros but for my needs its just what I needed at a good price.

The design has changed a bit but the ice tea maker reminds me of my grandma who had a Mr. Coffee iced tea maker in the 80's or maybe early 90's, but anyhow I bought it mostly for nostalgia along with sometimes wanting to make ice tea quickly in the winter when its too cold out to use the sun. I have used it a couple times now and it works great, the water is very hot, brews quickly. No complaints at all.

I was hoping this pump would be more powerful then the one I currently use but it wasn't this one despite it being more powerful according to the specs on the box pumped less air, and it was far more noisy as well, overall was not happy with it.

review_title: Old school is sometimes the best.
reviews: This might be an old school filter but sometimes old school is the best way. It's simple yet effective, perfect for when all you need is something basic and easy to use.

review_title: I did not find that it worked.
reviews: Didn't work for me.
Check valves are pretty basic, this one works and that's all that really matters.

I use this sand in several tanks, I really like the look, texture and size, its not messy and doesn't cloud the water too badly, rinses quickly. Great product. I know some say it requires a lot of rinsing but this isn't what I found, I did a quick rinse in a 5 gallon bucket for about 3 minutes and put into tank, very little cloudiness and cleared within the hour.
I needed this to make some holes in plastic for a DIY aquarium filter, I can't say how it works for its actual intended purpose but for my needs it worked and I had no issues.
I have used this brand for several years, its a good tubing for the money, stays soft and doesn't harden like other types can. Always been happy with this product.

Our little dog loves these small king squeak toys, I don't know what it is about them but they are by far her favorite toys. We have a few that are a couple years old and still holding up well, our dog isn't a destroyer of toys though. We have always been happy with the kong squeak toys as is our dog.

review_title: Just what I was looking for
reviews: Excellent product and just what I was looking for to build a fluidized bed filter.

review_title: Have bought a few of these now
reviews: I have bought 4 of these over the last couple of years and the oldest one is still working without issue, the cord is nice and long and for the price is pretty good build quality. The best feature is the long cord.

review_title: Seems like a good product so far
reviews: I have not been using this product long term yet, so this review is based on short term use, so far happy with this item, it made well for the price point, the fan is quiet, I cannot tell its even on its so quiet, seems to be doing a decent job keeping my laptop cooler.

I use a laptop and always frustrated with the built in speakers but didn't want to pay a fortune for speakers, found these and decided to give them a try and they work awesome and excellent value for the price, they look good, and seem to be well made. If your looking for a basic speaker, these are them.
I like this keyboard, and so far working flawlessly. Recommend.

For being a small light its a very bright light. I have had this light in my 15 gallon for a few months now, the suction cups at first worked fine and the light stayed in place for months, but now maybe week before the light is in the water, so suction cups like many don't seem to have a long life, but the light itself is still working great and grows low light plants well.
I love these badges, they are a good quick way to see if there is an ammonia problem, they work well and easy to use.

review_title: One of the best aquarium products
reviews: One of the best media for an aquarium, keeps water crystal clear, lasts a good amount of time and of course can be recharged several times so the price is really good considering you will get multiple uses from it. I run purigen in all my aquariums both freshwater and marine.
I really love this product, works well, light weight, easy to use. Quality product.

I am really liking this camera, not being a professional I find it an easy to use camera, with good instructions on how to use it, its not complicated at all and so far I really like it. I will update in a few months time once I have used it more and see if anything pops up that changes my mind.
Nice selection of colors. Decent quality for the price. Fits well.
The bottle does work, just doesn't keep liquids cold all that often, and is made of fairly thin plastic, basic and does work but not the best out there.

Working in a loud environment and having to wear hearing protection for hours a day, comfortable is important and these meet the task. I found this easy to put in and comfortable to wear and they provide a good amount of protection against loud noises. One of the better ear plug brands I have found.
Nice watch for the price, comfortable to wear, no issues whatsoever with this watch. Would recommend.
I wore this hat all summer at work, nice hat did its job.

This is a short term review and I will update once the toner cartridge has been in use for a bit.

The cartridges seem well made, they fit perfectly into my Dell printer without any issues. The print quality thus far is good and just as good as the original Dell cartridge that came with the printer.

There was no issues installing the cartridge.

I have only printed 20 or pages with it since receiving so longer term will be interesting to see how it works, but for now I am happy with this cartridge and its priced nicely as well.

Updated: Dec 24, 2018

The toner is still going strong after almost 3 months of use, keep in mind this is household use not commercial use, so I have only maybe done 200-250 pages, but still working good.
Does the job.

Decent price.

Only tools needed is the one it comes with and a screw driver.

Plastic handles.
Holes not drilled for some of the hardware.
Good surge protector for the price, works well.

review_title: Did what I needed it to do.
reviews:
I have an aquarium light that could not connect to the home wifi network, and moving the router wasn't an option, so figured I would give this a try. I have been using it for a week so far and it's worked fine, provides the boot to the signal that I need, was easy to set up as well, took just a few minutes to set it up and get it working. I can't vouch for long term as it's been just a week, but so far I am happy with this purchase and the product is working as described.

I'll update in the future after I have used this item for a few months.

review_title: Good frame, not difficult to assemble.
reviews: Not difficult to put together, but does take a bit of time, but overall easier then most boxed furniture. Just go slow and be patient and it's not too difficult. I like how it sits high, allows for plastic storage containers to be placed underneath it. Fits our Endy queen mattress perfectly. Seems well made, and is quiet. No squeaking sounds and doesn't move around on the hardwood floors like some frames tend to do. Decent price. Just a basic bed frame if your not needing anything fancy, I would recommend giving this one a try.

review_title: Price is okay, but they keep me a little too warm.
reviews: These sheets are okay, but do keep you on the warm side when sleeping. They are comfortable enough for the price, but if I were to decide again, I would go with a 100% cotton sheet.
It's tide. I am sure just about anyone has heard of tide and knows how well it cleans.

I have been using this device for several weeks now, seems to work well, seems accurate and is easy to use and set up. I was deciding between this one and the more expensive ones, and in the end I am happy with this one. Why pay more if you don't need to?
Good wipers. I am pretty impressed with these wipers. They do an excellent job, one of the better wipers I have used.

review_title: Nice but fits on the small side.
reviews: I like it, and quality seems decent, but the sizing is a bit off, seems to fit on the small side.
Good quality for the price, good shredder for the home, also cuts credit cards which is nice.

review_title: Best to look for another phone.
reviews: Have had this phone for about 6 months now, it works but has some issues that are annoying like not connecting to the line when there is nothing wrong with the line and the other phone works fine, it can do this for hours sometimes, very annoying. Suppose for the price it's fine, but not an item I would recommend.

review_title: I see it works for some, but I didn't notice any benefit to using this product.
reviews:
I think there are too many variables in the storage and shipping process for this product to consistently work. Seems some have no issues with this product and others like myself find that it did not do anything, certainly didn't speed the process up, and I would never add life to the aquarium relying on this product to do the job they claim it does. I was doing a fish-less cycle, followed the directions exactly as the manufacturer states on their website, and never saw any indication this product was working. On the Dr Tim's website they state one and only will last 6 months at room temperature's 65 to 85F and 1 year at cooler temps 50F, however the expiry date on the bottle I received is 8 months from now, and certainly doubt Amazon is keeping this product at 50F, so seems to be you may end up with nothing but overpriced water and bacteria if you receive an older batch, and of course we have no idea what temps the product has been exposed to in shipping, it wasn't below freezing at the destination, but who knows in route as it took 4 days to arrive, so maybe it was frozen in shipping?

If there was a store who sold it locally and I could get a new batch, I would give it a go again, but with shipping there simply seems to be too many variables that can end up killing the bacteria and thus the product not working.

I ended up just getting some established live rock rubble from another hobbyist with an established tank, this all around method seems to be the best way to seed a tank.
Loving it.,
It works as it should to increase ammonia in an aquarium for the cycling process.
It works, it's accurate and easy to use.

I find this rain suit of decent quality for the price, I wear it several times a week riding a scooter and I arrive dry. No issue so over the last couple of months, for the price I am happy, and as it keeps me dry, I cannot complain.
Not as described, very poor item, I do not recommend.
Good basic tool kit.

Nice light. I was having issues finding replacement for the track lighting in my condo as the ones in the stores locally did not work, thought I would give them one a try and it fits and works perfectly, much nicer then the originals as well, and I like how the fixture is for normal light bulbs and not some fancy expensiveness type like some of these fixtures require.
Wax was easy to use, and brought a nice shine to the car. Would recommend this product.
Good.
Been using this mouthwash for several years. I have found it's one the best on the market, doesn't have alcohol and doesn't dry my mouth out. Does what it's supposed to and no complaints from me.

review_title: First impression, good item and worth trying.
reviews:
First impressions based on a few days use. The cover seems well made, it is clear for those who might want to know, its not white. So far so good, but only time will tell, so will update the review after a few months use. For the price, at the moment I would give this item a thumbs up.

The screen cover seems good as well, it was easy to put on, cut correctly and fits the phone perfectly. Again will update after a few months.

Update 11/13/17

The screen cover is starting to come off, lasted about 2 months.

review_title: Seems like a well made decent jacket so far.
reviews: Nice jacket. Seems well made.

Seems like a solid well built lock and chain. Very heavy as well, the lock + chain runs a little over 10 pounds, so may not be the ideal choice if riding a bike, but I am using it with a scooter so can keep it in the scooters storage and it's not so bad. I guess there is no real way to know how strong the chain and lock is until someone tries to break in, but at first appearance and reputation of the company, seems like a very well made and secure product.
Have been using these for a couple weeks now, so far so good. Comfortable, and they stay put when using them. Will update after a few months use.
I really like the colors and easy to apply.
Excellent coffee.
Good item.
Works perfect. No issues.

Updated July 19, 2017. These knee pads start out well, but they don't hold up well with daily use and wear out quickly, and the velcro straps are also falling apart, better to spend a bit more upfront if you need a daily knee pad for work, these would probably work well for occasional use such as working around the house.

I work at an airport loading planes and use these when in the belly of aircraft and they work well. Comfortable to wear and no more sore knees.

Good product at a good price.
Works as intended. Good product and washes off easily with a bit of soap and water. No skin irritations from using it.
I really love this mascara. It doesn't clump on my lashes, and make my lashes look fuller and longer and goes on nicely. I will certainly be buying this mascara again.

Good product, works well so far, seems well built.

Will update review after a few months use.
I really liked this book, easy, fun read.
I like this coffee, nice flavor.
A very nice coffee. I will buy again.
I've always been a fan of Tide and these pods are excellent at getting clothes clean just like regular tide in the bottle is. No complaints from me, excellent product.
Used cascade for years, really like these pods. Gets dishes clean.
So far so good. Produces a nice wall of bubbles. Seems well made and a good price. I will update in a few months.
Item is of good quality and well made. Perfect for an aquarium RO unit.
We loved this peanut butter, excellent taste and quality made.

I use matrix in all my freshwater aquariums and find this to be an excellent product and provides good service area for the biological filter without needing a large amount. I run 2 containers in my canister filter. Very nice product.

I had ordered the wrong size and requested a return but amazon told me to keep these, so I did, and I have used them in the one and only device I have that takes AAA batteries, the batteries seem well made and of just as good quality as any of the name brand ones but of course at a more cost effective price point. They work well, however I am not using them in a high drain device so I can't comment on how they would work in such a device, but I don't see any flaws in these batteries, and they by no means feel cheap, or made cheaply, they very much seem very well made, and they worked perfectly right out of the package.
Excellent product in my view, have been using this product for several years without any issues.

Its a sediment filter, it does its job and keeps the system from clogging up with sediment. These are well made and work well. I use it in a RO/DI system for a reef tank, and these work well and at a better price point then most aquarium stores that sell them.
Item works have have been using it for months now and its holding up well, for the price, I have no complaints.

review_title: Okay at first but found after several days its not consistent.
reviews:
I got this for the noise & vibration mode and it works, seems of good quality and came as described. I wont use the shock option but did try it on my arm, and man does it ever shock, wouldn't personally want my dog to experience the shock mode, but the vibration mode is noticeable and gets the dogs attention.

Update: After a few days of using, I have found the product to be inconsistent, I'll press the button to make the noise of vibrate and the dog is just a few feet away and it doesn't activate, or it will activate 20-25 seconds after I press the button.

It's a power bar. It works, nice long cord. For the posts about it not being lit, this is true there is no light but per the manufacturers website this model is not supposed to have one so it's not a flaw, its simply not supposed to have a light.

Update: By far one of the best power bars for the price, it works well, feels well made, and the cord length is awesome, allowing the bar to be hidden if desired behind furniture or like in my case allowing the TV to be in a better location where there was no outlet 2-3 feet away.

review_title: Seems to do as it's supposed to.
reviews: Easy to use for the most part, only issue I have found is the color can be a little hard to read but overall a good test kit.

I really like this salt thus far. I've used it a couple times so far, and when I have tested the freshly mixed water, the calcium, ph, alkalinity are all spot on what Red Sea says they should be. Mixes really well and quickly. I was using reef crystals prior to this and found it didn't mix well and left a fair amount of residue, where this salt leaves no residue and mixes super fast. So far so good, and I am glad I spent a bit more to give it a try.

Ill update the review as time goes on and I have more long term experience with it, but so far so good.

Update: October 7, 2016- I have now used the entire first bucket and the tank is doing great and better then it did with instant ocean, and this salt is so much quicker to mix. I have now bought a 2nd bucket, first bucket lasted me about 2 months. 14 gallon nano.

I've had this pump before and they are top notch. Works perfectly in my 10 gallon cube, and is so much easier to hide smaller then the Fluval Sea stock circulation pump which is a lot bigger and more difficult to hide, I will be buying another to replace the Fluval one as 2 pumps work better then 1 at keeping up good flow on the display side.

For the price point this is the best circulation pump you will find in my opinion.It's also not made in China like a lot of aquarium items are, but made in Italy which seems to provide a better quality product overall.

I don't find the 240 bad for a 10 gallon cube when used in conjunction with another pump, not sure I would use just 1 240 in a 10 gallon and up though, but I always use 2 smaller pumps vs 1 larger one so I can get more random flow and for my purpose this size is perfect.

Amazon's price was a bit higher, but with being a Prime member it still came out cheaper then another online store who was 3 dollars cheaper but would have charged 9 in shipping so despite the higher price on Amazon, it was cheaper in the end.

It's a medication, I can't really review it accurately as I used it as a preventive in a quarantine tank for new arrivals, they never got sick, but can't say if the medication had anything to do with that though.

review_title: Good Products, works perfect for my needs.
reviews:
I have not put it in use yet but did test them, no leaks so so far so good. I bought this product at it was better price then buying 2 stand alone canisters. The metal part on top is easily removable and the 2 canisters can be detached from one another to become 2 separate canisters.

I am using one for the sediment filter, then the 2 on the original RO unit will have a carbon block each, and then the 2nd one from this unit will have the DI resin, and finally water into the bucket.

I see no difference between this item and more expensive ones.

Only downside is it only comes with two 1/4" quick release and for what I am doing I need 4, but no big deal, just ordered the size I needed on Amazon.com. The unit comes with a few different size connections of 2 each, but would be nice if they let you choose the size you need and how many, would cut down on waste as I don't need the other sizes for anything so likely will end up in the trash.

Good item for adding on to an existing RO unit, or if you just need a sediment and carbon block but no RO membrane.

No complaints, and I consider this a good product.

Update: I have had this unit a couple months now and still going strong, no issues at all.

review_title: Good, dog uses it, they don't leak.
reviews: For the price they are good, and the price point is good. Compared to the pet stores ultra high prices, these are a perfect compromise. Dog uses them, they don't leak all over the place, and they are an affordable price, will be buying again.
Still working almost 3 years later, works well, no issues.
Nice oil. Good quality.

review_title: Save time and money, don't buy this.
reviews: Was no good, poorly made, did not work. Ended up returning it.
They are pop tarts, they taste like pop tarts, same as the store but better price.

I bought this light as I read decent things about it on various forums, and the photos of tanks with it, looked awesome. So when I saw it on sale on amazon I decided to give it a go since the stock light on the Fluval M40 is no good.

This light is awesome, provides plenty of options, makes the colors of the fish and corals pop, fairly easy to use and set up through either the website or phone app.

The only down side is the fact the company who makes it does not include anyway to mount the light, so you have to pay another $40 or so for the mount. But the light is nice, looks well made, feels well made, and so far so good.

I will update this review in a couple months once the light has been running.

Update: Sept 3, 2016

As time has passed this item becomes less and less accurate and the screw to calibrate it also has become near impossible to turn.

Overall, I would say long term this item is not consistent nor accurate. Works great at first then starts to go wonky with time.

So far so good. Seems to work just as good as the pricey "pet store" branded ones. Honestly I think these may all be made in the same place, but who knows. I do know this works, and is easy to use and calibrate. I am glad I opted for this one rather then spending 65 dollars at the local fish store, this one looks identical to the one they are selling, I cannot tell any difference between the 2.

I know another review said it had no instructions included in English, however mine came with detailed instructions in English on how to use and calibrate the device. If you don't see instructions check under the foam in the storage case as that is where mine was, kind of hard to see but they should be there under the foam, but even without instructions google how and it will be more or less the same, simple turn of a screw and some distilled water,.
It works as advertised.

review_title: Not worth it. Get a Tunze or another well known brand with a long history in making skimmers.
reviews: After trying to get this thing to work, it's either defective or just junk. I expect some micro bubbles, but not at the rate this thing makes them, never had a skimmer produce so many bubbles before. It also doesn't have a good seal around the collection cup, so bubbles and water leak out there, and it skims pretty poorly.

review_title: Plants are health and growing well, good product.
reviews: Plants have never been healthier, I add 1/2 the dose once a week and so far after a couple months of use, good plant growth and color and no issues with algae.

review_title: Better then the originals that came with unit.
reviews: They work, they fit, very basic item so not much to review.

I realized with some searching online you don't need the entire kit that is sold for a higher price if your like me and already have more test tubes then you will ever need, so bought the replacement instead and simply found the instructions online, far more cost effective way to get some of these tests when all you need is the reagent.
It's a battery, it works, so what more can you ask for.
Does the job. Quality is better then the original elbows that came with the unit I have. (unit not made by this company) so no complaints.
Not the easiest kit to use and read the results, also found the directions to not be all that clear.
Does the job. Good value. No complaints.

Works well, good value. The reading it gives is consistent with what the monthly city water reports so seems to be working perfectly. I've used pricier models in the past and this one seems just as good as those. So far no complaints at all.
So far so good. Seems to work well so far. Quality seems good. Only been running a few days but will update if anything goes wrong. Seems to be better quality then name brand ones like Fluval.
Dog actually doesn't mind this product and will finally let me brush her teeth.
